data.description: This home is simply fabulous!! The architectural design, the interior layout, the location, and the price are all fantastic. The covered front porch with stone columns will welcome you in to a large living room with vaulted ceilings, a gas fireplace, and new carpet. The open dining area has sliders to a stamped concrete patio where you can relax and enjoy the peaceful view. The beautiful kitchen includes tons of cabinets and countertop space, an eat at bar, tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances (including a wine/beverage cooler), and a pantry. A laundry room and a convenient half bath complete the main level. Upstairs you'll find the primary suite with double entry doors, a full bathroom with double sinks and a walk-in closet, 3 additional nice sized bedrooms and a hallway bathroom. The lower level has an egress window, is stubbed for a bathroom, and could easily be finished for more living space. Additional amenities include ceiling fans in all the bedrooms, a large (20x6.5) storage space in the garage, an irrigation system, low Windsor Township taxes, and a new roof in November 2023 (complete tear-off and replacement because of wind damage). Some minor settlement cracks in the foundation walls are being repaired by the builder's warranty and will have a transferable lifetime warranty.
